headline: Is TransDigm Group Incorporated (TDG) Among the 10 Largest Defense Stocks in 2025?
summary: TransDigm Group Incorporated (NYSE:TDG) is among the 10 Largest Defense Stocks in 2025. Several analysts have slashed the stock’s price target in recent weeks amid ongoing government shutdowns. Morgan Stanley’s Kristine Liwag, on October 15, lowered TDG’s price target to $1,600 from $1,750. The analyst told investors that leading defense stocks were poised to report […]
